191,"age":10,"year":"1315","toYear":"1317","julianDay":2201354,"title":"Famine Strikes Europe","description":"A famine caused by cold winters and wet summers across Europe caused millions to die due to starvation. Desperation from hunger caused high levels of crime, stampedes in bread lines in London, infanticide, and even cannibalism throughout Europe.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705192,"age":23,"year":"1328","julianDay":2206102,"title":"First War of Scottish Independence","description":"The First War of Scottish Independence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705193,"age":32,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Robert De Plecy was born about 1305, in Shapwick, Dorset, England. He had at least 1 son with Mrs Robert De Plecy."},"et":{"Abt 1305–":"umbes 1305–Surnud","1310–Female":"1310–Surnud","1340–1440":"1340–1440","1305–Male":"1305–Surnud","1305":"1305","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1453":"1453","1310":"1310","1440":"1440","1340":"1340","Abt 1305":"umbes 1305","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Shapwick, Dorset, England":"Shapwick, Dorset, England"},"fi":{"Abt 1305–":"noin 1305–Kuollut","1310–Female":"1310–Kuollut","1340–1440":"1340–1440","1305–Male":"1305–Kuollut","1305":"1305","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1453":"1453","1310":"1310","1440":"1440","1340":"1340","Abt 1305":"noin 1305","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Shapwick, Dorset, England":"Shapwick, Dorset, England"},"fr":{"Abt 1305–":"environ 1305–Décédé","1310–Female":"1310–Décédée","1340–1440":"1340–1440","1305–Male":"1305–Décédé","1305":"1305","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1453":"1453","1310":"1310","1440":"1440","1340":"1340","Abt